asses of cytokines including IL-4 and IL-13.  Once CN phosphatase activity is inhibited, dephosphorylation of NFAT and subsequent nuclear localization of NFAT decreases, which results in a decrease of NFAT/AP-1 complex formation at the cytokine promoter sites (Rao et al. 1997).", "timestamp": "Mon Jun 08 14:54:16 +0000 2026"}